        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "But he should, at the same time, brave the responsibility of declaring that, in his opinion, he understands their principles better than they did themselves; and especially should he not shirk that responsibility by asserting that they \"understood the question just as well, and even better than we do now.\"",
