        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "In that case, only about twenty were admitted to the secret; and yet one of them, in his anxiety to save a friend, betrayed the plot to that friend, and, by consequence, averted the calamity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
