        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "In that supposed event, you say, you will destroy the Union; and then, you say, the great crime of having destroyed it will be upon us!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
