        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000070_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "That is cool.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000071_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000071_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "To be sure, what the robber demanded of me my money was my own, and I had a clear right to keep it; but it was no more my own than my vote is my own; and the threat of death to me, to extort my money, and the threat of destruction to the Union, to extort my vote, can scarcely be distinguished in principle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000072_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000072_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "Let us Republicans do our part to have it so.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000072_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000072_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "Even though much provoked, let us do nothing through passion and ill temper.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000073_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000073_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "We know they will not.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000073_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000073_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "In all their present complaints against us, the Territories are scarcely mentioned.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000073_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000073_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "We know it will not.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000074_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000074_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "Simply this: We must not only let them alone, but we must, somehow, convince them that we do let them alone.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000074_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000074_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "This, we know by experience, is no easy task.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000074_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000074_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "In all our platforms and speeches we have constantly protested our purpose to let them alone; but this has had no tendency to convince them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000075_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000075_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "These natural and apparently adequate means all failing, what will convince them?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000075_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000075_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "And this must be done thoroughly-done in acts as well as in words.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000076_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000076_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "They will continue to accuse us of doing, until we cease saying.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000077_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000077_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "Demanding what they do, and for the reason they do, they can voluntarily stop nowhere short of this consummation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000078_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000078_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "If slavery is right, all words, acts, laws, and constitutions against it are themselves wrong, and should be silenced and swept away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000078_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000078_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "If it is right, we cannot justly object to its nationality its universality; if it is wrong, they cannot justly insist upon its extension-its enlargement.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000078_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000078_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "All they ask we could readily grant if we thought slavery right; all we ask they could as readily grant, if they thought it wrong.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000078_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000078_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "Their thinking it right and our thinking it wrong is the precise fact upon which depends the whole controversy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-340_124368_000078_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/340/124368/340_124368_000078_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-340",
        "content": "Thinking it right, as they do, they are not to blame for desiring its full recognition, as being right; but thinking it wrong, as we do, can we yield to them?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    }
]